com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.wrappers

Class RenderOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.wrappers.RenderOptions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BlockRenderOptions, ItemRenderOptions

    public abstract class RenderOptions
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String>, java.lang.Cloneable
    Stores information used at render time when drawing blocks. Render hints such as shape and orientation are stored using this type. This type is safe to use in HashMaps for efficient look-ups.
